thread.title_full: Majestic Star Casino reviewed by T Moser

author: T Moser
title: T Moser
text: By Far the Best Video Poker around! A lot more variety of games, higher payouts & better odds than any casino in the area. The buffet is awesome, great lake views. I especially love the Friday special grilled Lobster... . And the Steel City Grill has BBQ Ribs to die for...take some home for later or just your late night snack. Have not yet tried the new Chop House but I'll bet it's a winner too.
